docs.flapjack-project.com
=========================

Builder for flapjack-project.com website. 

Triggered as a GitHub Post-Receive Hook, it will checkout
the latest copy of the Flapjack source code, generate new HTML
for the flapjack-project.com website, and move it in place.

Configuring
-----------

1. Set up this directory as an Apache VirtualHost with Passenger. 
2. Run `rake deps` to freeze dependencies.
3. Edit WEBSITE_DIR and CHECKOUT_DIR in server.rb to taste.
4. Run `ruby test-post.rb` to do a test post.


